Aspect            | Compile Time                                 | Run Time
When it happens   | Before program runs                          | While program is running
Purpose           | Translate/check code                         | Execute code
Type of errors    | Syntax, type errors (in static languages)    | Logic, runtime exceptions
Tools used        | Compilers, linters                           | Interpreter or OS
Fixable B Run     | Yes                                          | No, needs to run first to see